 <div class="section-a">
   <p>Barber is an app that allows time-poor
   Men to summon a professional 
   Barber to the comfort of their homes. The 
   service promises that a customer will be under 
   the blow-dryer 
   within half an hour of tapping on their smartphone 
   screen.</p>
   <img src="https://tallypress.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/top-10-barber-shops-in-kl-selangor.jpg">
 </div>
 
 <div class="section-b">
   <p>When a customer asks for a hair cut through the 
   app, the request will go to the salons within a
   one-mile radius. The first salon to respond will be 
   sent an Uber car that will despatch a barber to the 
   home or hotel address and then return him to the salon. 
   The stylists will come armed with a range of hair
   products</p>
   <img src="http://www.greatbritishbarberingacademy.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/11/IMG_7224-copy.jpg">
 </div>
 
  <div class="section-c">
   <p>The consumer gets the convenience of a 
   hair treatment on demand in the privacy of
   their own home, hotel or office. The salon 
   will gain access to thousands of potential 
   customers in their vicinity who may want to 
   use their
   services, but may not have known about their 
   offering</p>
  </div>
  
